| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0751 — Recovery Inhibition (vicesociety)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d9f55371-6753-5dd5-9a87-7dad9c4d571e"
